    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. This car has been my pride and joy, and it shows in its overall presentation. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professional touch-up on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seats with only light creasing on the driver's bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has followed a strict synthetic oil change schedule every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It recently passed a full multi-point inspection and sits on a set of Michelin tires with plenty of tread remaining. Included are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a folder of service receipts. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
